com.vanillasource.gerec.reference

Class MediaTypeAwareResourceReference

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vanillasource.gerec.reference.MediaTypeAwareResourceReference
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ResourceReference, Serializable

    public abstract class MediaTypeAwareResourceReference
extends Object
implements ResourceReference
    Implement all media-type related functionality (serialization, deserialization) and request modification. Subclasses "only" need to implement the direct HTTP related functionality.
    See Also:
